        {
            "title": "內地A股早市顯著回吐 芯片相關板塊成重災區",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">隔晚美國芯片及半導體股急回，拖累日韓等科股成分重的股市，滬深股市亦顯著回吐，芯片相關板塊沽壓明顯，兆易創新(03986)A股(603986.SH)逾9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"兆易創新招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03986.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"兆易創新招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03986.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">兆易創新招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早初段一度跌69點或1.68%，低見4,043點，其後跌幅迅速收窄，半日高位4,093點時跌幅縮至18點0.46%，早市大部份時間跌幅不足1%；滬指中午收報4,075點，跌37點或0.9%，半日成交1.02萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指昨天已率先回吐，今早繼續相對跑輸，甫開市即失守萬六關，最低曾見15,575點，跌543點或3.37%，雖然其後跌幅漸見收窄，但半日高位15,886點時仍跌232點或1.44%；深指中午收報15,782點，挫336點或2.09%，成交1.22萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也跌91點或1.85%，收報4,867點；創業板指數挫147點或3.47%，報4,112點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250409_FI_source-ap_AShare-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250409_FI_source-ap_AShare-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">早前備受追捧的兆易創新，今日一度失守700元關口，低見699元，跌9.46%；中午收報701.18元，仍跌9.17%，半日成交已達260.3億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其餘芯片及半導體相關股亦普遍向下，瀾起科技(06809)A股(688008.SH)跌9.08%，報287.22元；華虹宏力(01347)A股(688347.SH)跌5.66%，報297.76元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)跌3.31%，報149.29元；AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)也跌5.75%，報1,400元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16284724-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e9%a1%af%e8%91%97%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e6%88%90%e9%87%8d%e7%81%bd%e5%8d%80",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250408_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 11:42:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股升454點後升幅收窄  車股跑贏  晶片及硬件股大幅回落",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股今早反彈，恒生指數早見22995，升114點或0.49%，為暫時低位﹐最高暫報23335，升454點或1.98%，但其後升幅收窄，現升201點或0.88%，報23082點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數報4500，升27點或0.62%  ; 恒生國企指數報7624點，升65點或0.87%，報7624點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交1827.35億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6 月汽車交付量理想，汽車股普遍造好，比亞迪(01211)升8.9%，報78.9元，為表現最佳藍籌股，貢獻恒指35點。6月銷量達40.35萬輛，海外出口創高。(02015)升3.47%，報47.68元 ; 吉利(00175)升3.5%，報17.45元 ; 零跑(09863)升3.71%報35.76元。小米(01810)也升4.16%，報22.54元，6月汽交付量超過萬輛。蔚來(09866)則跌1.91%，報38元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">生科醫藥股揚升，信達生物(01801)揚7,41%，報85.55元 ; 石藥(01093)升6.89%，報7.45元 ; 翰森製藥(03692)升6.14%，報31.44元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片及AI股隨外圍回落，中芯(00981)瀉9%，報81.35元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 華虹宏力(01347)挫9.49%，報194.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">建滔積層板(01888)插13.06%，報86.2元 ; 建滔(00148)升9.16%，報107.1元 ; 智譜(02513)插14.54%，報1798元; MINIMAX(00100)瀉10.65%，報372.6元 ; 長飛光纖(06863)跌16.76%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facebook母公司Meta Platforms計劃出售人工智能(AI)運算能力和模型的使用權，引發市場AI過度投資的憂慮，此外部份AI模型股禁售期滿，引發該類股份沽壓。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16284545-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87454%e9%bb%9e%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e8%bb%8a%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%91%e8%b4%8f-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e5%8f%8a%e7%a1%ac%e4%bb%b6%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 11:16:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
